{"tid":2078933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Black Lives Matter] 貝多芬竟然是黑人","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T12:36:08.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad84e74e3b501066b06977b8c8ad53fe922ba4b4","tid":2078933,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabKtSX.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaabKtSX.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=5cab3913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貝多芬是歷史上著名的音樂家之一，儘管他聽力下降仍然堅持創作，還留下許多名作，後世也尊稱他為「樂聖」。<br />\n不過這位音樂家竟然還莫名捲入最近吵超兇的「#黑人的命也是命 Black Lives Matter 」抗議事件當中，因為竟然有傳聞他其實是黑人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eaw273CX0AA2CSW?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEaw273CX0AA2CSW%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=bf5285d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起源都來自這一篇推特，推主附上了證據截圖，並且聲稱貝多芬其實是非洲後裔！並表示在18-19世紀時貝多芬只要出席社交場合都會將臉塗白，還有在別人替他畫肖像畫的時候找來白人替身，就連歷史學家也幫忙隱瞞關於貝多芬真實血統的真相，這篇充滿爆點的推文隨即引起許多人討論。<br />\n<br />\n其實這篇文章出自於2015年，針對貝多芬是黑人提出兩點原因，一是他google發現有許多關於貝多芬「厚嘴唇、寬而扁的鼻子和深色皮膚、黑頭髮和小眼睛」外型特徵的敘述，加上他的母親來自於摩爾人區，因此更大幅增加了貝多芬可能有黑人血統的要素。<br />\n<br />\n原作者表示自己雖然不是音樂史專家，但歐洲人自古以來都有將歷史偉人「洗白」的嫌疑，他認為提出這個議題相當重要，可能會接露歐洲殖民主義者對於掩蓋真實歷史的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1273472307718021123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273472307718021123&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=7b2f9255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273472307718021123&h=1f4842dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1273472307718021123</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1273623883376136195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273623883376136195&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=65c462a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273623883376136195&h=d4f9030c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1273623883376136195</a>"},{"pid":"104b5fba77f0e8da0056666574c551cc01b17ac0","tid":2078933,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:59:24.000Z","msg":"Racist<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342749f899eb91ed55f7dde8f1029a838d0cda6a","tid":2078933,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"係都唔出奇，大仲馬都有黑人血統。"},{"pid":"8c07408d470e2dabc6019e328d9f887c448965f2","tid":2078933,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:12:43.000Z","msg":"其實已前歐洲得黑人"},{"pid":"34adc2526525ff21cc44551d9129ec8261ba6b36","tid":2078933,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"但係貝多芬唔作Rape歌"},{"pid":"c69e381dc97ba63d4ecaa36daea1caf6fd1ac41c","tid":2078933,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"342749f899eb91ed55f7dde8f1029a838d0cda6a","tid":2078933,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"係都唔出奇，大仲馬都有黑人血統。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:24:45.000Z","msg":"係都唔出奇，包青天都有黑人血統"},{"pid":"b45380d7a2f803deaed32bd11e3e4b02326c8983","tid":2078933,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"黑人聽貝多芬個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身黑人都歧視白人，blm去到尾聲會唔會轉返做wlm"},{"pid":"37917b68a922c6d44633453d90f4be69f46bbce3","tid":2078933,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"全世界都係黑人咪無歧視囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f13e8c2b0f7b4013eb5a79a5f747446c69c0ba","tid":2078933,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quot